Missions.MagicTournament.Title: Clovers Tournament
Missions.MagicTournament.Rules1: Make combinations of 4 or more candies to earn Clovers!
Missions.MagicTournament.AnimationMainTe: You are so kind! Mooo! I’ll make the best milk now! Thank you and enjoy the prize!
You almost did it! Thank you for gathering clovers for me. Don’t worry, you will win the prize next time!
Clover makes milk so tasty! I wanna make the best milk in the Candyland.
That’s why I need so much clover leaves! Let’s see who can get more!
Missions.RoseTournament.Title: Diamond Rush
Missions.RoseTournament.Rules1: Collect as many Diamonds as you can to become a Diamond King!
Missions.RoseTournament.AnimationMainTex: Ooh! You really tried your best! Diamonds are so shiny! Take this as a reward for your effort!
Ooh, it’s not enough for me! I need more. I hope you’ll try harder next time!
I am the Dragon, the Lord of Diamonds! I’m looking for fearless travelers to collect as many diamonds as they can!
Are you one of them? I have an amazing reward for the top collectors!
Missions.TulpanTournament.Title: Snacks Boom
Missions.TulpanTournament.Rules1: Match sweets next to the snacks to collect them!
Missions.TulpanTournament.AnimationMainT: Woof! You’re my best friend and a lord of snacks! Woof! Woof! Take your prize!
Woof! I've got some snacks, thanks! Don’t worry about the prize, you’ll get it next time!
Woof! I like snacks so much! I am arranging a contest for the players!
Woof! Bring me as much snacks as you can and you might get a very special prize!
Valentine.Missions.TulpanTournament.Rule: Match sweets next to the roses to pick them!
Valentine.Missions.TulpanTournament.Anim: Amazing! This bunch of roses will make so many people happy! Here, take your prize!
Thank you! I'll make sure to deliver these roses! Good luck with the prize next time!
Everyone loves flowers! Let's pick them together and spread the joy around!
So many people want to help me! If your contribution to the cause is substantial I'll make sure to honor it with a reward!
Memorial.Missions.TulpanTournament.Title: Summer Bloossom
Memorial.Missions.TulpanTournament.Rules: Match sweets next to the flowers to pick them!
Memorial.Missions.TulpanTournament.Anima: I can't believe my eyes! All these flowers are mine! You were incredible out there and here is your well-deserved reward!
Thank you! Your effort means a lot to me but these are not enough to celebrate summer. Better luck next time!
There is no better time to pick flowers than summer! Let's pick them together to celebrate the start of this wonderful time!
Unfortunately, there are not enough flowers for everyone! Help me pick as many as possible and I'll make sure to return the favor!
